description:
The Great Irish Bake Off - Season 1, Episode 3




Paul Kelly and Biddy White Lennon challenge the remaining contestants to create an Irish bread basket composed of Soda bread, Irish tea bread and a non-yeasted bread for the signature bake.
In the technical bake, the amateur bakers must recreate Paul's tear and share Party bread.




Original Air Date: 03-Oct-2013
